item.title: Addressing the Backlash - Was I wrong about Anarchy Online?
item.description:
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/joshstrifehayes Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/joshstrifehayes Discord: https://discord.gg/GM2sCUX Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/joshstrifehayes Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/joshstrifehayes
#####
It should go without saying but do not harass any of the Anarchy Online community.
This video was made in response to the overwhelming negative feedback from the AO community, and is an earnest attempt to learn the game, and objectively critique the mechanics, while discussions AO's place within the MMO world.
Thank you to the supporters on Patreon and Twitch who keep this channel alive.
